    <mxCell id="stage4" value="&lt;b&gt;Stage 4&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;DATA MERGE ENGINE&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;Source Authority Matrix:&lt;br&gt;• ATS wins: name, phone&lt;br&gt;• GitHub wins: skills&lt;br&gt;• LinkedIn wins: headline, edu&lt;br&gt;• CSV wins: years_exp&lt;br&gt;Lists: union + dedup&lt;br&gt;All provenance retained&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#1a1a2e;strokeColor=#e94560;fontColor=#ffffff;fontSize=12;arcSize=10;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
